title: Food Prep

description:

Corinne is an EXPERT at teaching beginners HOW to start food prep. This episode covers: How to know what meals to start with. The first step to take in your kitchen so you are ready to go. How I organize myself with utensils, cutting boards, and pans. You'll find this episode jam packed on how to be ready for the week so you cut the excuses to not eat healthy.
